      acceptedAnswer: { '@type': 'Answer', text: 'For weight loss, 1-2 servings of protein gummies per day as between-meal snacks is the typical recommendation. Each serving provides 10-15g of protein, contributing to daily protein targets (0.7-1.0g per pound of body weight for active adults in a calorie deficit). Time them strategically: one serving mid-morning and one mid-afternoon when hunger and cravings peak. The total daily calorie contribution (120-240 calories from gummies) should be factored into your daily caloric target, not added on top of it. Protein gummies are not a replacement for protein-rich meals — they supplement your protein intake during the gaps between meals when you are most susceptible to unhealthy snacking.' },
    },
